_sText:
base map for a mapping contest.
This map is based on defrag style. I've spent a lot of effort designing and building this map (hopefully not in vain, and you will like it).

There are many ways to get through. Suitable for all bhop styles, even S-only haha =)).

Any player, from beginner to professional, can complete the map. There are no checkpoints or triggers on the map, except for boosters. But this provides even more alternative routes.

Long map
tier 1-5 =))

Happy game =)
